                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I noticed the hare's foot when I found it; it was quite saturated with turpentine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MRS. HANAFORD</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> A person named Davis, who is here, came to the Church, and gave me information of the fire.</p>
