               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. CLARKSON</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Were you passing the door, hearing the alarm, or seeing the fire, did you go in? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I went in, and asked the prisoner where his mistress was—he told me she was at church, and I went to the church to fetch her.</p>
